<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>webdav on 路飞博客</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/webdav/</link><description>Recent content in webdav on 路飞博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 18:49:40 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/webdav/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Openwrt安装alist和阿里云盘webdav</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/openwrt%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85alist%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98webdav/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 18:49:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/openwrt%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85alist%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98webdav/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>以下插件只适用于斐讯 N1,其他没测试过&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="一-使用方法">一: 使用方法&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>下载插件,然后进入软路由: &lt;code>系统&lt;/code>&amp;ndash;&lt;code>文件上传&lt;/code>&amp;ndash;&lt;code>安装&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>例如: 斐讯 N1 盒子软路由&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="二-阿里云盘webdav插件">二: 阿里云盘webdav插件&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>插件下载:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/woniu336/openwrt-ipk/tree/master/N1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98webdav" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/woniu336/openwrt-ipk/tree/master/N1安装阿里云盘webdav&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>项目地址 : &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="三alist插件">三:Alist插件&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>OpenWrt 查看CPU架构命令：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cat /etc/os-release &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>grep ARCH
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>插件下载:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/woniu336/openwrt-ipk/tree/master/N1%E8%BD%AF%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85alist" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/woniu336/openwrt-ipk/tree/master/N1软路由安装alist&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>项目地址 : &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/sbwml/luci-app-alist" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/sbwml/luci-app-alist&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>AList文档：https://alist.nn.ci/zh/guide/&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="四-docker-安装阿里云盘webdav">四: Docker 安装阿里云盘webdav&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker run -d --name&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>aliyundrive-webdav --restart&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>unless-stopped -p 8080:8080 &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -v /etc/aliyundrive-webdav/:/etc/aliyundrive-webdav/ &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">REFRESH_TOKEN&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;your refresh token&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">WEBDAV_AUTH_USER&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>admin &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">WEBDAV_AUTH_PASSWORD&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>admin &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> messense/aliyundrive-webdav
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>其中，&lt;code>REFRESH_TOKEN&lt;/code> 环境变量为你的阿里云盘 &lt;code>refresh_token&lt;/code>，&lt;code>WEBDAV_AUTH_USER&lt;/code> 和 &lt;code>WEBDAV_AUTH_PASSWORD&lt;/code> 为连接 WebDAV 服务的用户名和密码。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Openwrt安装阿里云盘 WebDAV</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/openwrt%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98-webdav/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 18:18:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/openwrt%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98-webdav/</guid><description>&lt;p>阿里云盘 WebDAV 服务，主要使用场景为配合支持 WebDAV 协议的客户端 App 如 &lt;a class="link" href="https://firecore.com/infuse" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Infuse&lt;/a>、&lt;a class="link" href="https://nplayer.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>nPlayer&lt;/a>
等实现在电视上直接观看云盘视频内容， 支持客户端 App 直接从阿里云盘获取文件播放而不经过运行本应用的服务器中转, 支持上传文件，但受限于 WebDAV 协议不支持文件秒传。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>请注意：V2 版本基于阿里云盘开放平台接口实现，不再支持阿里云盘 Web 和 App 版本获取的 refresh token。&lt;/strong>
&lt;strong>由于本项目作者不再使用梅林固件，V2 版本不再免费支持 Koolshare 梅林固件系统，如有需要请考虑&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/discussions/778" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>付费支持&lt;/a>。&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="安装">安装&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>可以从 &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>GitHub Releases&lt;/a> 页面下载预先构建的二进制包， 也可以使用 pip 从 PyPI 下载:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pip install aliyundrive-webdav
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果系统支持 &lt;a class="link" href="https://snapcraft.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Snapcraft&lt;/a> 比如 Ubuntu、Debian 等，也可以使用 snap 安装：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo snap install aliyundrive-webdav
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="openwrt-路由器">OpenWrt 路由器&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>GitHub Releases&lt;/a> 中有预编译的 ipk 文件， 目前提供了
aarch64/arm/mipsel/x86_64/i686 等架构的版本，可以下载后使用 opkg 安装，以 nanopi r4s 为例：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases/download/v2.3.2/aliyundrive-webdav_2.3.2-1_aarch64_generic.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases/download/v2.3.2/luci-app-aliyundrive-webdav_2.3.2_all.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases/download/v2.3.2/luci-i18n-aliyundrive-webdav-zh-cn_2.3.2-1_all.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">opkg install aliyundrive-webdav_2.3.2-1_aarch64_generic.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">opkg install luci-app-aliyundrive-webdav_2.3.2_all.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">opkg install luci-i18n-aliyundrive-webdav-zh-cn_2.3.2-1_all.ipk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>其它 CPU 架构的路由器可在 &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/messense/aliyundrive-webdav/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>GitHub Releases&lt;/a> 页面中查找对应的架构的主程序 ipk 文件下载安装， 常见
OpenWrt 路由器 CPU 架构如下表（欢迎补充）：&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th>路由器&lt;/th>
&lt;th>CPU 架构&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>nanopi r4s&lt;/td>
&lt;td>aarch64_generic&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>小米 AX3600&lt;/td>
&lt;td>aarch64_cortex-a53&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>斐讯 N1 盒子&lt;/td>
&lt;td>aarch64_cortex-a53&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>Newifi D2&lt;/td>
&lt;td>mipsel_24kc&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>Pogoplug&lt;/td>
&lt;td>arm_mpcore&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Tips: 不清楚 CPU 架构类型可通过运行 &lt;code>opkg print-architecture&lt;/code> 命令查询。&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/09/ab37d11644e919f925437a1008c2a593.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="Pasted image 20230914182516"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="docker-运行">Docker 运行&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker run -d --name&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>aliyundrive-webdav --restart&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>unless-stopped -p 8080:8080 &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -v /etc/aliyundrive-webdav/:/etc/aliyundrive-webdav/ &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">REFRESH_TOKEN&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;your refresh token&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">WEBDAV_AUTH_USER&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>admin &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -e &lt;span class="nv">WEBDAV_AUTH_PASSWORD&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>admin &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> messense/aliyundrive-webdav
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>其中，&lt;code>REFRESH_TOKEN&lt;/code> 环境变量为你的阿里云盘 &lt;code>refresh_token&lt;/code>，&lt;code>WEBDAV_AUTH_USER&lt;/code>
和 &lt;code>WEBDAV_AUTH_PASSWORD&lt;/code> 为连接 WebDAV 服务的用户名和密码。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="qnap-威联通-nas">QNAP 威联通 NAS&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="qnap-插件">QNAP 插件&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/iranee/qnap-aliyunpan-webdav" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>qnap-aliyunpan-webdav&lt;/a> by
&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/iranee" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>@iranee&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="containerstation-docker">ContainerStation (Docker)&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>管理员登陆 NAS 后安装 ContainerStation 并启动服务，在 Management (管理) 标签中 Create Application (新建应用)，配置如下&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">version&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;3.3&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">services&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">aliyundrive-webdav&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">container_name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">aliyundrive-webdav&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">restart&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">unless-stopped&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;8080:8080&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">environment&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;REFRESH_TOKEN=mytoken...&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">messense/aliyundrive-webdav&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>其中 &lt;code>REFRESH_TOKEN&lt;/code> 文档最下面说明；&lt;code>:8080&lt;/code> 网盘访问映射端口，可以按需改为其他的。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>点击 Create (创建)后启动，访问 http://nas地址:8080/ 即可看到你网盘的自动生成索引网页文件。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考文档&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://docs.docker.com/compose/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://docs.docker.com/compose/&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.composerize.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://www.composerize.com/&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="rclone">rclone&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>为了避免重复上传文件，使用 rclone 时推荐使用 &lt;a class="link" href="https://rclone.org/webdav/#nextcloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Nextcloud WebDAV&lt;/a> 模式，可以支持 sha1 checksums.
另外需要配合 &lt;code>--no-update-modtime&lt;/code> 参数，否则 rclone 为了更新文件修改时间还是会强制重新上传。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>举个例子：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rclone --no-update-modtime copy abc.pdf aliyundrive-nc://docs/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="获取-refresh-token">获取 refresh token&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://messense-aliyundrive-webdav-backendrefresh-token-ucs0wn.streamlit.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>通过在线工具获取 refresh token&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>命令行运行 &lt;code>aliyundrive-webdav qr login&lt;/code> 扫码授权后会输出 refresh token&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
